snippet.title: Mixture - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Here's your look at combat, ferocious enemies, and more in this trailer for Mixture, an action-adventure self-co-op VR game where you control two characters simultaneously -- Sola, The Moth Knight, and The Alchemist. Mixture will be available on PlayStation VR2 on February 6, 2024, and it is available on Meta Quest.
